    allowing the init netns to set the default algorithm to one that is restricted. This restriction could be
    removed if tcp_allowed_congestion_control were namespace-ified in the future. This bug was uncovered with
    https://github.com/JonathonReinhart/linux-netns-sysctl-verify (CVE-2021-47010)

